<li><a href="http://toxnet.nlm.nih.gov/cgi-bin/sis/search/r?dbs+hsdb:@term+@rn+@rel+7439-97-6" class="external text" title="http://toxnet.nlm.nih.gov/cgi-bin/sis/search/r?dbs+hsdb:@term+@rn+@rel+7439-97-6" rel="nofollow">NLM Hazardous Substances Databank – Mercury</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.globalmercuryproject.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.globalmercuryproject.org/" rel="nofollow">UNIDO/UNDP/GEM Global Mercury Project</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.epa.gov/ostwater/fishadvice/advice.html" class="external text" title="http://www.epa.gov/ostwater/fishadvice/advice.html" rel="nofollow">EPA fish consumption guidelines</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.atsdr.cdc.gov/tfacts46.html" class="external text" title="http://www.atsdr.cdc.gov/tfacts46.html" rel="nofollow">ATSDR — ToxFAQs™: Mercury</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.webelements.com/webelements/elements/text/Hg/index.html" class="external text" title="http://www.webelements.com/webelements/elements/text/Hg/index.html" rel="nofollow">WebElements.com – Mercury</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.jtbaker.com/msds/englishhtml/m1599.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.jtbaker.com/msds/englishhtml/m1599.htm" rel="nofollow">Material Safety Data Sheet – Mercury</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.theodoregray.com/PeriodicTable/Elements/080/index.s7.html" class="external text" title="http://www.theodoregray.com/PeriodicTable/Elements/080/index.s7.html" rel="nofollow">Hg 80 Mercury</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.chem.unep.ch/mercury/Report/Final%20Assessment%20report.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.chem.unep.ch/mercury/Report/Final%20Assessment%20report.htm" rel="nofollow">Global Mercury Assessment report 2002</a> by the <a href="./United_Nations_Environment_Programme" title="United Nations Environment Programme">UNEP</a>.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.greenfacts.org/mercury/index.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.greenfacts.org/mercury/index.htm" rel="nofollow">A summary of the UNEP report</a> by <a href="./GreenFacts" title="GreenFacts">GreenFacts</a>.</li>
